L'Aquila.title: L'Aquila
L'Aquila.byline: L'Aquila is the capital of the province of the same name in the region of Abruzzo in Italy and is located in the northern part of the province.

L'Ange-Gardien.title: L'Ange-Gardien
L'Ange-Gardien.byline: L'Ange-Gardien is an eastern suburban municipality of Quebec City, in Quebec.
